            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* NASA Science delivers an estimated 3-to-1 economic return on investment, benefiting the broader commercial aerospace sector in Colorado\n* Funding request adheres to the National Academies' Decadal Surveys, ensuring non-partisan, peer-reviewed scientific priority-setting\n* Strong alignment with bipartisan congressional support and allied organizations like the American Astronomical Society and American Geophysical Union\n* Maintains U.S. global leadership and the ability to set international norms for 21st-century space exploration and discovery",
